NXTBee - Class in lejos.nxt.addon
Send and receive data using a Dexter Industries NXTBee attached to Port 4 The NXTBee uses a RS485 serial link.
NXTBee() - Constructor for class lejos.nxt.addon.NXTBee
Default constructor initialises a NXTBee object at 9600 baud Enables the internal data reading thread
NXTBee(boolean) - Constructor for class lejos.nxt.addon.NXTBee
Constuctor for the NXTBee running at default 9600 baud.
NXTBee(int, boolean, boolean) - Constructor for class lejos.nxt.addon.NXTBee
Constructor to create a NXTBee object to communicate at a specified baud rate and to select if the internal data reading thread is running.
